text_blocks.snippet: Calf Manna is a multi-species performance-enhancing supplement designed to help animals of various ages and breeds reach their peak condition. It provides high-quality protein, digestible carbohydrates, and essential vitamins and minerals to support growth, energy levels, and overall health. It's known for its palatability, with anise flavoring, and is used to help animals stay on feed during stressful situations.
snippet_highlighted_words: a multi-species performance-enhancing supplement designed to help animals of various ages and breeds reach their peak condition

list.title: Performance Enhancement:
list.snippet: Calf Manna is formulated to improve an animal's overall performance, helping them achieve their full potential in terms of growth, muscle development, and energy levels.

list.title: Multi-Species Use:
list.snippet: It can be fed to a wide range of animals, including horses, cattle, rabbits, goats, poultry, swine, and deer.

list.title: High-Quality Protein:
list.snippet: Calf Manna contains multiple sources of high-quality protein, which are essential for growth and muscle development.

list.title: Digestible Carbohydrates:
list.snippet: The digestible carbohydrates in Calf Manna provide a readily available source of energy, making it suitable for weight gain and supporting animals during periods of stress.

list.title: Palatability:
list.snippet: The inclusion of anise, a flavoring agent, enhances the palatability of Calf Manna, encouraging animals to consume it even during stressful times.

list.title: Stress Management:
list.snippet: It helps animals stay on feed during stressful situations like travel, illness, or environmental changes.

list.title: All Life Stages:
list.snippet: Calf Manna is suitable for animals of all ages, from young foals and calves to older animals.

list.title: Improved Coat Condition:
list.snippet: Linseed meal, an ingredient in Calf Manna, is known to improve the coat condition of animals.
